Uses of Package
entity

  • Packages that use entity 
    Package Description
    Controller
    Contains java classes that manage the interactions between entities and DAO java classes
    DAO
    Contains java classes that only interacts with the database
    entity
    All java classes that do not belong to the other packages
  • Classes in entity used by Controller 
    Class and Description
    BootstrapStat
    A class which contains validated data from the CSV files

    correctRows - ArrayList<String[]> of validated records in the CSV file
    bootstrapErrors - ArrayList<BootstrapError> of errors in the CSV file
    fileName - Name of CSV file
    numRecords - number of correct records in the CSV file
    rowNum - HashMap<String,Integer> for UserLocationController, rowNum is a hashmap for containing the timestamp + macaddress and the row number of that particular row to check for duplicates
    Companion
    A class for storing intervals spent by a companion at each location
    durationOfEachLocation - Time spent at each location.
    Group
    A class which contains the groupings of all Companion classes
    commonLocationInterval - common intervals spent by all companions in the group
    grouping - list of all companions in the group
    minTimePerLocation - minimum time spent by all companions in the group
    totalTime - total time spent by the group
    Location

    numOfPeople - number of users in the particular location(semantic place)
    semanticPlace - location name
    macaddress - macaddress of user in that location
    timestamp - interval time spent by user in that location
    User

    macAddress - macaddress of user
    name - name of user
    email - email of user
    password - password of user
    gender - gender of user
    admin - true if user is an admin, false if otherwise

    Class and Description
    BootstrapError

    Row number of the error in the CSV file
    Types of errors within one error message
